{"tid":1739281,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藝人鬧理大校長呼喚學生","createTime":"2019-11-19T14:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T14:51:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f26420069a85360ae454f46722d2f9abad3b297d","tid":1739281,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191119/20808896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F20808896&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=6fe2b224\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F20808896&h=418c864b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191119/20808896</a><br />\n<br />\n藝人鬧理大校長呼喚學生<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083538_3627.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083538_3627.gif&h=a349ea79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伍家謙<br />\n<br />\n警方前日開始在理大與抗爭者對峙，有多人受傷及被拘捕，情況慘烈，人人呼籲和理非聲援理大，藝人們都不例外，挺身公開發聲救理大。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：皓騫、陳杰<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：導演鄧卓儒疑被補<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083535_80ae.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083535_80ae.gif&h=9686f40c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083535_fbc1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083535_fbc1.gif&h=fe3581e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王宗堯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083536_f528.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083536_f528.gif&h=62513e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBen Sir<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/large/1574083537_5934.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574083537_5934.jpg&h=6da13c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃秋生<br />\n<br />\n黃秋生昨日在twitter貼片：「Please help HK！」之後接受《蘋果》訪問時說：「拉晒全香港人啦，𠵱家已經係戰爭，唔係抗爭。」前晚警方狂拉現場義務急救員，秋生不屑：「人道危機上國際法庭，同情都係罪。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191119/small/1574083538_f2c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191119%2Fsmall%2F1574083538_f2c4.jpg&h=82ce55a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n港台《頭條新聞》主持曾志豪：「希望香港人救救理工大學嘅大學生，希望我哋嘅警察，你唔好忘記，佢哋係我哋香港嘅年輕人，係我哋嘅下一代，政權，唔好將自己變成一個屠夫政權，對話，唔好再對抗。」 <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林夕斥香港掌權人破壞法治<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n校友邵仲衡梁芷珊籲救學生 鄭敬基理大外食催淚彈「好擔心年輕人性命」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n導演鄧卓儒疑被補<br />\n<br />\n導演鄧卓儒疑被補<br />\n林夕斥香港掌權人破壞法治<br />\n校友邵仲衡梁芷珊籲救學生鄭敬基理大外食催淚彈「好擔心年輕人性命」"},{"pid":"ee833d2420859ce625022fcec8b9db290d2617bb","tid":1739281,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d423258dd430cefd12e8dcd6b2de9c1be000c78","tid":1739281,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"黎黎去去都係嗰幾個"}]}